@NODE "Main" "VCON"


@{B}                       VCON a Telnet Daemon for the Amiga
                                 By Marcus Käll
                              version 0.4 [1998/12/09]
@{UB}

VCON is a telnet daemon which makes it possilble for other users
to login to your Amiga using a telnet application. From version
0.3 it also supports devices, so users can login from the serial
line too. VCON supports both usergroup and multiuser login system,
you can also turn off the login. It emulates the con: quite well,
read more about the exceptions under limitations


